Experimental GTK Contacts Browser app
--------------------------------------------------------------
Experimental PyGTK contacts browser app.   
Works by using the Python GTK and Evolution bindings 
to render and display your Evolution contact data in a 
Mac OS X style contact browser application.

To run the app:
$ python mycontacts.py

All GUI resources are defined and maintained in the 
corresponding mycontacts.glade GLADE file.

Prerequisites
--------------------
* Python 2.5+
* Evolution
* Python evolution, gtk, gobject, pango, bluetooth bindings
* Python vobject module (from Chandler project)
